    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-02-17T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-02-17T19:00:00-05:00" n="25"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d25">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.34/255: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-02-17T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >February 17, 1942—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>111. Your 100, February 9, noon. The Navy Department states that it sees no
                    objection to the transfer to the Chinese Government of the U. S. S. <hi
                        rend="italic">Tutuila</hi> together with its equipment and stores. The Navy
                    Department is initiating action to carry out the transfer under <pb facs="0033"
                        n="23" xml:id="pg_23"/> the provisions of “Defense Aid”. It is understood
                    that, without obtaining additional specific legislative authority, there is no
                    other available method of effecting the transfer.</p>
                <p>The Chinese Embassy is being informed of the foregoing, with the request that the
                    matter be considered as confidential until the transfer has been actually
                    effected.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
